510
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:15,200
You're not my mommy!

511
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:45,398
Guys, how would you like

512
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,137
to eat dinner in front of the television

513
00:28:47,138 --> 00:28:48,900
for a whole week?

514
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:59,300
What are you guys doing here?

515
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:05,600
Kayla, stop screaming!
you're hurting my ears!

516
00:29:05,700 --> 00:29:07,900
Get in the car!

517
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:11,000
Come on! We're going home!

518
00:29:11,100 --> 00:29:12,600
Get your seat belt on!

519
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:15,300
Kids-- They're always roughhousing.

520
00:29:35,800 --> 00:29:36,900
Why'd you stop?

521
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:41,800
Well, uh, it's getting late.
I got your blouse unbuttoned.

522
00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:43,800
