523
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:47,300
Do you wanna call it a night?

524
00:29:48,500 --> 00:29:50,400
What, do you wanna grab
a pizza or something?

525
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:01,700
I wanna do what...
you wanna do.

526
00:30:02,900 --> 00:30:04,500
Well...

527
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:06,000
You know what I wanna do.

528
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:09,600
Well, okay.

529
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:12,000
Are you sure?

530
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:14,900
Yeah, I'm sure.

531
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:37,241
You can always spot the new guys

532
00:30:37,242 --> 00:30:39,000
by the way they pick through their food.

533
00:30:42,500 --> 00:30:44,859
So what did you do when you
thought no one was looking?

534
00:30:46,100 --> 00:30:47,900
The cops say I kill a woman.

535
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:49,600
But you didn't, right?

536
00:30:51,562 --> 00:30:54,200
Actually I have no idea.

537
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:57,800
I got pretty banged up in an accident.

538
00:30:58,500 --> 00:31:00,800
