539
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:04,300
Well that's a fresh approach.

540
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,000
I'm not sure the jury's
gonna swallow it.

541
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:08,300
It's the truth.

542
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:12,700
I believe you.

543
00:31:17,111 --> 00:31:19,699
Okay, Mrs. mccluskey's downstairs,

544
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:22,199
