the street if you need us.

545
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:23,300
Okay, daddy.

546
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:27,949
You know, I heard what happened
with Lynette today.

547
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:33,100
Hey, she's doing her best.
Why you being so hard on her?

548
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,800
'cause it's her fault
my mommy died.

549
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,899
No. no, no, honey. It's not.

550
00:31:37,900 --> 00:31:39,399
Mom only went to that store

551
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:41,092
because Lynette was trying to steal me.

552
00:31:41,093 --> 00:31:42,616
Okay, that it is not true.

553
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:45,789
Look, honey, it is way more

554
00:31:45,790 --> 00:31:47,500
complicated than that.

555
00:31:49,100 --> 00:31:50,899
I know you miss your mommy,

556
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:53,100
and she loved you very much.

557
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:55,000
But guess what?

558
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:58,100
Lynette loves you too.

559
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:02,100
That's why you gotta give her a chance.

560
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,500
Can you do that for me?

561
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:09,200
Okay. i'll be good.

562
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,500
That's my girl.

563
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:14,500
But I'm never gonna love her...

564
00:32:16,415 --> 00:32:17,900
And you can't make me.

565
00:32:32,700 --> 00:32:34,000
Well, you've won.

566
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:36,000
What did I win?

567
00:32:40,300 --> 00:32:41,558
Bill and I split up.

568
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,800
Can't say I'm surprised.

569
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,000
He wasn't right for you.

570
00:32:46,500 --> 00:32:47,300
I know.

571
00:32:48,808 --> 00:32:51,300
So just admit you sent the flowers.

572
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:53,600
I didn't.

573
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:56,373
Carlos, just tell me.

574
00:32:56,374 --> 00:32:58,400
I won't be mad. I promise.

575
00:32:59,698 --> 00:33:01,260
Gaby, if I was gonna send you flowers,

576
00:33:01,261 --> 00:33:02,800
I wouldn't send you
pink roses.

577
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,700
I'd send you white orchids,

578
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:07,600
Because I know they're your favorite.

579
00:33:09,500 --> 00:33:12,500
And if I wanted to
cheer you up sunflowers.

580
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:14,100
and for the flu...

581
00:33:16,100 --> 00:33:17,300
Blue irises.

582
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:31,800
I hate that you know me so well,

583
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:34,199
and it took so long for that to happen.

584
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,700
